{"tid":2125030,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"政府否認推禁足令  男子涉發假消息被捕 議員憂網禁首例","createTime":"2020-07-26T01:39:59.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-26T03:02:43.000Z","uid":25558,"like":3,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"f281d56ef7929c6fa2e2606819477a7b4d423b15","tid":2125030,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-26T01:39:59.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20200726/DGOOATL2LD4REQDN3H7S337SIM/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200726%2FDGOOATL2LD4REQDN3H7S337SIM%2F&d=OqPbpPrVkTbcBhMc%2F4HaLt5k9s62d79lhUbErROZgj4%3D&h=8314b102\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200726%2FDGOOATL2LD4REQDN3H7S337SIM%2F&h=6e66574c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20200726/DGOOATL2LD4REQDN3H7S337SIM/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n政府否認推禁足令 <br />\n男子涉發假消息被捕 議員憂網禁首例<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】日前政府。。。。。。。。。。。<br />\n。。。有立法會議員擔心案件為警方「網禁」開先例，製造白色恐怖，並質疑以政治取態左右執法標準，要求清楚交代涉案假消息內容。<br />\n<br />\n。。。。。。。。。。。涉嫌干犯《簡易程序治罪條例》下「使用無線電話傳送虛假訊息」罪。。。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/fgxZr3C-80t2iA9Cb4ioHcfL5ts=/640x640/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/SQABWYAAZBTON4UU2RCDFH5JGU.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FfgxZr3C-80t2iA9Cb4ioHcfL5ts%3D%2F640x640%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FSQABWYAAZBTON4UU2RCDFH5JGU.jpg&h=7c8dc56a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n林卓廷揶揄警方否認警暴，亦屬發佈假消息。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n林卓廷：拉PPRB發言人先啦<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：鄧達智感染 曾與徐小鳳飯敍<br />\n<br />\n網罪科警司譚威信。。。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/L_gjPF-8o0sh9xyKbeXDHHQCZgQ=/640x360/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/QQNIFTUS3FCVSO6ZD2AFZMUGBQ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FL_gjPF-8o0sh9xyKbeXDHHQCZgQ%3D%2F640x360%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FQQNIFTUS3FCVSO6ZD2AFZMUGBQ.jpg&h=147150d3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n網罪科警司譚威信（右）昨指警方拘捕一名發放假消息的男子。<br />\n<br />\n民主黨立法會議員林卓廷認為，警方必須「講清楚嗰啲乜嘢係假消息，究竟係傳言，抑或蓄意揑造謠言出嚟令人相信，從中獲利定係點呢？」他揶揄警方：「講到發佈假消息，警方都經常做㗎啦，咁多事情涉及警暴，佢哋都一概否認，甚至誣衊受害人&hellip;&hellip;應該先拉咗警察公共關係科好多發言人先啦！」<br />\n<br />\n公民黨立法會議員郭家麒直言，「好擔心開咗呢個先例&hellip;&hellip;係白色恐怖，亦係萬能key，可以拉好多人。」他反問林鄭及陳肇始之前稱武漢肺炎疫情受控，又稱豁免檢疫人士沒影響疫情，但結果疫情失控，日前專家亦分析第三波疫情最有可能源自多宗輸入個案、早前豁免檢疫的人員等，「咁林鄭同陳肇始講嘅係唔係假消息？」"},{"pid":"8af212f54168ecec3af7a0631c2badf5aa9f3326","tid":2125030,"uid":45975,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-26T01:40:48.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"5c35c8c710f85314663b4033a8050f5cedf54b86","tid":2125030,"uid":56819,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-26T01:41:03.000Z","msg":"痴線,同大陸有咩分別"},{"pid":"7243d1430d15cebbc02c93119d0e685db3cfaec3","tid":2125030,"uid":77196,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-26T01:44:57.000Z","msg":"有案例唔可以用呢條罪入，班狗係咪弱智<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"de43f54d62cb4da9f498026c9e3b6bfa1bd3d43e","tid":2125030,"uid":20870,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-26T01:46:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />自己發放假消息就得"},{"pid":"784e821101272be52378ee89e481ea4024b568dd","tid":2125030,"uid":58841,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-26T01:48:19.000Z","msg":"班狗係咪弱智<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b3c2c73c1295337a64b897aacd1d8f95e79d8a7d","tid":2125030,"uid":60000,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"f281d56ef7929c6fa2e2606819477a7b4d423b15","tid":2125030,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-26